- Ian Mckellen爵士
- 不行

26
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:00,900
Justin Bieber
Justin Bieber. Yes?

27
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,100
行吗

28
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:05,000
就他了
He'll be fine. Marvellous.

29
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,900
非常好

30
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:12,200
我们带来了一件复制品
