plenty of time to prepare.

32
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:18,900
你从Justin手中接过来
So, you pick up from Justin,
then it's up the steps

33
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:21,100
走上台阶 就这么简单

34
00:01:20,556 --> 00:01:23,532
and Bob's your uncle.
