因为我是他的小公主
And he says I can have whatever
I want, because I'm his princess.

42
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:40,000
没错 你的确是
Yes, you are.
So, all we need now is
your sponsorship cheque. Of course.

43
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:44,300
现在只差你的赞助支票了

44
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,500
没问题

45
