很好 这真是莫大的荣幸
Good. Well, it's been an
absolute pleasure. How exciting!

46
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:00,000
多激动人心啊

47
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:04,900
Lucinda一定会气疯的
Lucinda will be completely sick.
All she's doing is a stupid dance.

48
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:07,100
她只能去跳那只傻得要死的舞

49
00:02:06,524 --> 00:02:09,552
She'll be one of hundreds,
but I'll be special.

50
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:09,500
她就是一群众演员
