51
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,500
没错 你会的 宝贝
Yes, you will, poppet.

52
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:14,200
那么接下来呢
So what happens now?

53
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,700
大概一周后 你就能收到所有的书面材料
All the paperwork will come through
in about a week or so - rehearsal
dates, VIP passes, details, etc.

54
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:20,400
