90
00:04:13,592 --> 00:04:16,576
She was such a brat.

91
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,800
她真是讨人厌的小贱人

92
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:18,100
是啊 所以国家才会被搞成这样

93
00:04:16,576 --> 00:04:19,572
Yeah... The way some people
bring up their children.

94
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:19,800
看看他们都怎么教孩子的

95
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:22,500
我在她这个年纪就只有
冰冻果子露和呼啦圈
All I had at her age was
a Sherbet Dib Dab and a hula hoop.

96
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:25,500
- 我每次都能轻松赢你
- 你吹牛的吧

97
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:26,504
I used to beat you hands down
every time. You bragging?

98
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,300
他们都叫我 水蛇腰肯尼迪

99
00:04:26,504 --> 00:04:29,548
Snake Hips Kennedy, they used
to call me. He was such a girl.

100
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:29,600
实际上 这名字是他自己取的
他就是小弱受啊

101
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,900
不就是因为我总能打败你嘛
Only cos I used to beat you.

102
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:33,400
没错 因为你一直不把
我的呼啦圈还给我 这就是原因

103
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:33,568
Yes, because I couldn't
get it off you, that's why.

104
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,800
好了 孩子们
All right, children - we've made
100 grand, you can all have hoops.

105
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:37,300
我们刚有了10万
一人一打呼啦圈就不嫌多

106
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:40,700
你确定Albert这个年纪
还转得动呼啦圈吗 要转出人性命来的
Sure that's wise at Albert's age?
He might do himself a mischief. Oh?

107
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:43,300
我就来教你们小年轻一两手吧

108
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:43,556
Well, I could teach you youngsters
a thing or two.

109
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:44,500
你可以的 Albert
Yes, you could.

110
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:46,800
- 我算是明白你们了
- 咋了

111
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:48,576
I've worked something out about
you lot. You're like big kids. Yeah?

112
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,800
- 你们就是一群小毛孩子
- 是吗

113
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:52,800
你说有了10万所以一人一打
呼啦圈的时候就整明白了
I realised when you said you had
a 100 grand so everyone
could have hoops.

114
00:04:52,544 --> 00:04:56,552
Who in their right mind,
if they had a 拢100,000,

115
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:54,400
哪个正常人会

116
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:57,900
想着用10万英镑去买呼啦圈

117
00:04:56,552 --> 00:04:58,556
would spend it on hoops?

118
00:04:57,900 --> 00:05:00,500
- Eddie 呼啦圈哪得罪你了
- 他可是呼啦圈代言人啊

119
00:04:58,556 --> 00:05:02,572
He's hoopist. Could've had
a bad experience as a child.

120
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:03,200
- 也许是小时候有什么阴影了
- 是啊 挥之不去啊

121
00:05:02,572 --> 00:05:06,516
Yeah, he got all tangled up...
Couldn't quite get the rhythm...

122
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:05,900
- 跟不上节奏什么的
- 我就是这个意思

123
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:08,400
看见没 你们就是一群
倒霉催的捣蛋鬼

124
00:05:06,516 --> 00:05:08,560
See? You're like big kids,
messing about...

125
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:12,000
你是有什么要说吗 Ed
还只是在乱吼一通
Are you making a point here, Ed,
or just having a Northern rant?

126
00:05:11,548 --> 00:05:13,528
There is a point, actually.

127
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:13,800
事实上 我是有事要说

128
00:05:14,564 --> 00:05:18,540
One of you did this to Rushie!

129
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:18,000
你们当中某个人对Rushie干了什么

130
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,500
等等 你怎么知道是我们干的
Hang on.
How do you know it was one of us?

131
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:25,700
因为是昨晚发现的
那是只有你们在这儿
Cos it happened last night,
and you were the only ones in here.

132
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:28,800
- 好吧
- 好吧 所以呢 是谁干的
Right. Right? So? Who was it?

133
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:32,300
不管是谁干的 他肯定不会画画
看看这胡子画得多糟糕
Well, whoever it was can't draw,
cos his moustache is rubbish.

134
00:05:31,576 --> 00:05:34,564
That's his real one.

135
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,900
那是他的真胡子

136
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,300
你们玷污了他 看看他
You've defiled him! Look at him!

137
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:37,500
可简直罪无可恕
It's not right, this!
This man was poetry in shorts.

138
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:40,200
他可是体育界的诗人

139
00:05:41,592 --> 00:05:43,576
Summat funny, Michael?

140
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:44,300
有什么好笑的 Michael

141
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:47,000
不好笑 对不起
No. Sorry.

142
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:50,300
好吧 除非有人承认
否则你们就是黑名单
Eh? Barred?

143
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,900
- 诶
- 黑名单？

144
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:55,100
- 这有点过了吧 Ed
- 是啊 我们可是合伙人啊
That's a bit strong, innit Ed?

145
00:05:53,576 --> 00:05:55,564
Especially as we're your partners.

146
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:57,700
你们平时取笑羞辱我就算了
I don't mind all the banter
and the general abuse,
but this is going too far!

147
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:59,100
但这个太过分了

148
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:02,300
好吧 我想最好有人承认
All right, I think someone
better own up.

149
00:06:06,552 --> 00:06:09,584
What you looking at me for?
Well, you're the football nut.

150
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:09,700
- 你们看着我干嘛
- 你是铁杆球迷

151
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:12,900
- 喂喂 又不是所有球迷都是流氓
- 反正不是我
Oi, oi, we're not ALL hooligans.
Well, it wasn't me.

152
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:16,700
够了 你们全都上黑名单
直到我找出是谁干的

153
00:06:13,504 --> 00:06:17,540
Right, well - you're barred, all
of you, till I find out who done it.

154
00:06:19,584 --> 00:06:21,524
I mean it!

155
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:21,900
我没开玩笑

156
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:29,300
- 走吧
- 走吧 快点
Let's go. Well, go on. Come on.

157
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,500
- 黑名单
- 黑名单
Barred? Barred!

158
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,000
说真的 伙计们
I'm serious, guys.
It's taken me years to teach Eddie
how to make a proper breakfast.

159
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,800
我花了好几年才教Eddie
做出像样的早餐

160
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,800
没错 更别说
失去我们的办公室了

161
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,596
Yes - not to mention
losing our office.

162
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:49,100
是啊 他那疯狂的利物浦球迷心
已经被点燃了
Yeah, well,
he's got that Scouse resolve.

163
00:06:48,572 --> 00:06:51,596
He won't give up till one of us
admits it.

164
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:51,800
除非我们中有人承认了
否则他不会放弃的

165
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:56,100
所以 到底是谁干的
So go on. Who was it?

166
00:07:04,532 --> 00:07:05,580
ALBERT COUGHS UNEASILY

167
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:08,592
I'm Spartacus. You?!

168
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:09,100
- 我有份
- 你

169
00:07:08,592 --> 00:07:14,576
I did the ears.
I er...I did the glasses.

170
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:12,900
- 我画了耳朵
- 我 厄

171
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:15,200
我画了眼镜

172
00:07:14,576 --> 00:07:16,576
And the beard?

173
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,300
那谁画的胡子

174
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:32,900
准备好了吗 看着
Ready for this? Watch.

175
00:07:33,532 --> 00:07:35,504
THEY ALL GIGGLE AND MUTTER

176
00:07:52,544 --> 00:07:54,516
(Hide the pen.)

177
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:55,700
看见没
See...?

178
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:58,400
嗯 这么做太幼稚了 不是吧

179
00:07:56,572 --> 00:07:59,596
Well, that wasn't very grown-up,
was it? Albert started it.

180
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,600
Albert开的头

181
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,700
- 嘿 你个小八卦
- 噢 得了吧 那根本就...
Hey, you snitch.
Oh, come on, don't even start.

182
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:03,900
行了 够了

183
00:08:02,536 --> 00:08:04,560
All right, that's enough,
that's enough.

184
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:06,000
我们晚点再担心Eddie吧

185
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:08,532
We can worry about Eddie later.
Albert's got a new mark. Oh, who?

186
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,200
- Albert找到了新目标
- 噢 谁

187
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:11,400
这个有点以公谋私了
It's er.. kind of personal.

188
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:14,800
Ash 能帮我一下吗
Ash, would you...help me out?

189
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:21,000
这是Dexter Gold 当然不是本名
This is Dexter Gold.
That's not his real name, he changed
it by deed poll four years ago.

