那是什么呢

1164
00:54:26,000 --> 00:54:29,200
你们深入敌后 先发制人
You get dropped behind enemy lines
to take people out.

1165
00:54:28,592 --> 00:54:32,584
Well, that's what I want you to do
to the German.

1166
00:54:29,400 --> 00:54:32,600
我也正想要你们这么对付那德国佬

1167
00:54:32,800 --> 00:54:34,700
把他挖出来
I want you to track him down for me.

1168
00:54:34,568 --> 00:54:37,500
His name is Heinz Zimmerman.

1169
00:54:35,100 --> 00:54:37,300
他叫Heinz Zimmerman

1170
00:54:37,500 --> 00:54:41,200
找到他 然后帮我好好照料他
I want you to find him,

1171
00:54:38,580 --> 00:54:41,532
and I want you to...
take care of him for me.

1172
00:54:41,200 --> 00:54:43,100
- "好好照料他"
- 你们懂的
"Take care of him?"
You know what I mean.

1173
00:54:43,100 --> 00:54:45,500
噢 对 好好照料他
Oh, yeah. Take care of him.

1174
00:54:46,300 --> 00:54:51,300
这一共五万磅 
把他带给我后再给五万磅
There's 50 grand there,
there'll be the same again

1175
00:54:49,572 --> 00:54:51,536
when you bring him to me.

1176
00:54:52,400 --> 00:54:57,600
或给我看...
他死后冰冷尸体的照片
Or show me a photo...
of his cold, dead body.

1177
00:55:06,100 --> 00:55:07,600
做不做
Do we have a deal?

1178
00:55:07,524 --> 00:55:09,548
Let me get this straight.

1179
00:55:08,100 --> 00:55:10,000
让我把话说白了

1180
00:55:11,000 --> 00:55:15,200
是不是我们找到Heinz Zimmerman
解决掉他
If we find this Heinz Zimmerman,
take care of him,

1181
00:55:15,600 --> 00:55:19,600
给出照片证明 你会再给我们五万
and show you a photo of that,
you'll give us another 50 thousand?

1182
00:55:21,500 --> 00:55:22,900
没错
That's right.

1183
00:55:29,572 --> 00:55:31,552
Then you've got a deal.

1184
00:55:30,200 --> 00:55:31,800
成交

1185
00:55:34,900 --> 00:55:36,400
你知道怎么联系我的
You know where to find me.

1186
00:55:46,900 --> 00:55:48,300
这不是真的吧
Did that just happen?

1187
00:55:50,700 --> 00:55:54,100
- 没错 是真的
- 刚我还以为我们有麻烦了
Yes, it did. I thought we were
in trouble for a minute.

1188
00:55:54,300 --> 00:55:57,500
不用担心 我搞定
Not to worry, I'm on it.

1189
00:56:12,552 --> 00:56:13,596
Wait a minute.

1190
00:56:13,200 --> 00:56:14,300
等等

1191
00:56:16,200 --> 00:56:19,300
呃 一定要在衬衫上撒番茄酱吗
Ugh, did you have to put ketchup
on this shirt?

1192
00:56:18,584 --> 00:56:22,528
With five grand, you can buy a new
shirt. You have to look the part.

1193
00:56:19,300 --> 00:56:20,800
五千磅可以买件新的了

1194
00:56:20,800 --> 00:56:22,300
你总得看着像回事啊

1195
00:56:22,300 --> 00:56:24,400
就是装死
Or dead to be precise.

1196
00:56:25,000 --> 00:56:27,400
知道 不 抓那里 抓那儿

1197
00:56:25,500 --> 00:56:27,520
OK, now, that. No.
Hold that, hold that.

1198
00:56:27,500 --> 00:56:30,500
太好了
That's fantastic.

1199
00:56:29,584 --> 00:56:31,560
I really missed you lot, you know.

1200
00:56:30,500 --> 00:56:31,700
我想死你们了 知道吗

1201
00:56:31,700 --> 00:56:33,700
是吗 我们也很想你 Ed
Yeah, well, we missed you too, Ed.

1202
00:56:33,700 --> 00:56:36,200
- 真的吗
- 是啊 别再抱我了
Did you?
Yeah. Just don't hug me again.

1203
00:56:37,500 --> 00:56:38,900
为西汉姆联队干杯
Here's to West Ham.

1204
00:56:39,300 --> 00:56:41,300
哦 干杯
Oh, cheers.

1205
00:56:45,576 --> 00:56:48,544
Hang on a minute, you're supposed
to say, "Here's to Liverpool."

1206
00:56:46,200 --> 00:56:48,800
等等 你应该说 "为利物浦队干杯"

1207
00:56:49,900 --> 00:56:50,900
为什么
What for?

1208
00:56:52,300 --> 00:56:53,300
噢 这太不对了吧 
Well, that's not very nice, is it?

1209
00:56:53,300 --> 00:56:57,100
你继续这样 那道歉还有什么意义

1210
00:56:54,500 --> 00:56:57,516
What's the point in apologising
if you behave like that?

1211
00:56:57,800 --> 00:56:59,200
但道歉的是Sean 我没有啊
But Sean apologised, I didn't.

1212
00:56:59,200 --> 00:57:01,500
- 有 你有
- 不 我什么也没干
Yes, you did.
No, I didn't do anything.

1213
00:57:01,500 --> 00:57:03,200
那张CD呢

1214
00:57:02,500 --> 00:57:03,504
What about the CD?

1215
00:57:05,300 --> 00:57:06,500
什么CD
What CD?

1216
00:57:10,300 --> 00:57:11,200
Ash的口信
'Message from Ash.

1217
00:57:11,200 --> 00:57:15,200
很抱歉我损坏了有史以来
最伟大球员的照片
'I'm sorry for defacing
the photograph

1218
00:57:13,536 --> 00:57:16,560
'of the greatest footballer
who ever lived. Ian Rush.'

1219
00:57:15,300 --> 00:57:16,500
Ian Rush

1220
00:57:16,600 --> 00:57:20,600
Ash...这我可以解释
Ash...

1221
00:57:17,564 --> 00:57:19,524
This...

1222
00:57:19,524 --> 00:57:21,532
this can be easily explained.

1223
00:57:22,400 --> 00:57:25,000
收一份钱 杀两个人怎样
How about two dead bodies
for the price of one.

1224
00:57:26,000 --> 00:57:27,800
不过一个是真死...

1225
00:57:26,500 --> 00:57:27,576
Only one of 'em will be real...

1226
00:57:28,800 --> 00:57:30,300
因为我要杀了你
..cos I'm going to kill you.

1227
00:57:30,300 --> 00:57:31,600
- Ash
- Sean 赶紧跑
Ash. Sean, just run.

1228
00:57:31,600 --> 00:57:34,000
别傻站了 快帮我
Don't just stand there! Help me!

1229
00:57:34,300 --> 00:57:36,600
Ash 别逼我做后悔的事
Ash, don't make me do something
I'm going to regret!

1230
00:57:37,500 --> 00:57:38,560
Argh!

1231
00:57:38,700 --> 00:57:41,300
太紧了 太紧了 Ash
That's pretty tight.
That's pretty tight! Ash!

